T1  - STRATEGIC RESPONSES TO INSTITUTIONAL PROCESSES
AU  - Oliver, Christine
Y1  - 1991/01/01
PY  - 1991
DA  - 1991/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1991.4279002
